<C>__{jamal}
<D>__{truth alone triumphs? i should have known better.}
<A>__{the inspector stops the jeep. unlocks the handcuffs. holds the back door open for jamal.}
<C>__{inspector}
<D>__{thought you might need a lift, sir.}
<A>__{he nods towards the outside world. dazed, jamal gets out.}
<L>__{exterior chhatrapati shivaji terminus. night.}
<A>__{jamal finds himself gazing up at vt station. slowly, he wanders inside. the inspector takes the contents of the file and tears them slowly in half. lets the pieces fall on the ground. gets back in the jeep and drives away.}
